                        </div>
    
</article>
            </li>
            </ol>
</article>

</div>


  
</section>

    

    
      

<section class="component  ">

  
  <div class="component-text-block">
  
    <div class="component-description">
                    <h2 id="policy-groups-internships-and-student-testimonials" class="__title visible">Policy Groups, Internships and Student Testimonials</h2>
                    </div>

  
  <p>We encourage our students to make a difference by participating in our student groups. The internship placement course allows our students to integrate classroom learning with practical experience in a real workplace environment.</p>



